name: Clean, Lightly Used Full-Size Serta Mattress (Capitol Hill, DC)
description:
I just put a Serta full-size mattress in the middle of the 600 Block of D Street, NE in DC.

It was our guest bed and got little use. It’s clean and in very good condition.

I will take it back inside if it starts to rain and will try to take down the ad as soon as somebody picks it up. First come, first gets it.
